snippet: He visited imperial palaces and construction sites. He presided at a Miss Universe pageant. He hobnobbed with city officials at gala functions and seemed to particularly enjoy dining on Russian sausage....

headline.main: Capello Not Surprised by Conte's Chelsea Success
headline.print_headline: Capello Not Surprised by Conte's Chelsea Success

lead_paragraph: He visited imperial palaces and construction sites. He presided at a Miss Universe pageant. He hobnobbed with city officials at gala functions and seemed to particularly enjoy dining on Russian sausage.
